name: Immodest
tagline: Universal modelling of galaxy structure in arbitrary sets of image data
body:
### Welcome

This is the next generation of the [MegaMorph](http://www.nottingham.ac.uk/astronomy/megamorph/) project.  It is currently in the early days of development by Steven Bamford (@bamford), but if you're interested in commenting or contributing please get in touch.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
